Title: Geometric quantisation of the global Liouville mechanics
Authors: Z. Bajnok, D. Nogradi, D. Varga, F. Wagner
Comments: 5 pages, LaTeX
Report-no: ITP-Budapest 543
Journal-ref: J.Phys. A32 (1999) 7477-7481
\\
  The reduced SL(2,R) WZW quantum mechanics is analysed in the framework of
geometric quantization. The spectrum of the Hamiltonian is determined, and it
is found, that contrary to the previous approaches, there is a unique,
physically preferred quantisation of the system.
